Summary: Glowing bright object speeding across sky.
divs: Sighting DetailsMy niece Sam alerted me of the ufo as it came to view.silently going at great speed across the sky.at the time I was exlplaining to her that it would be rare to see a ufo,so I got binoculars out to look at the moon being the anniversary of the moon landing.just at that moment Sam screamed out look Tim and to amazement this glowing object darted across the sky.after the sighting we went back in all exited to tell my wife Mary,but she thought we were kidding her.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Beckenham
This sighting has never been favorited.
